WEBVTT

01:39.479 --> 01:43.360
[Road to Success]

01:54.400 --> 01:55.280
Your family member has arrived.

01:55.280 --> 01:56.740
You can be discharged now.

02:18.240 --> 02:18.770
Brother.

02:20.000 --> 02:20.910
Have you collected all his medication?

02:20.910 --> 02:21.750
Yeah, I have.

02:21.750 --> 02:22.560
Make sure he takes it on time.

02:22.560 --> 02:23.360
Okay. Thanks.

02:24.560 --> 02:25.160
Thank you.

02:34.590 --> 02:36.680
Brother, give me my phone.

02:42.240 --> 02:46.610
[Lin Dewen]

02:42.850 --> 02:44.210
Dear Mr. Lin,

02:45.010 --> 02:47.480
regarding your daughter, Lin Wanxing...

03:16.740 --> 03:18.750
[Episode 24]

03:21.560 --> 03:23.680
Why don't you take the chartered bus back?

03:23.680 --> 03:24.840
You've used up too much energy.

03:24.840 --> 03:27.100
Don't go to the high-speed rail station.

03:27.120 --> 03:28.310
I think I'll still
take the high-speed rail.

03:28.310 --> 03:29.750
That way I can get some rest.

03:29.750 --> 03:31.430
Just admit you're afraid of
getting carsick.

03:31.430 --> 03:33.630
Why make excuses about wanting to rest?

03:35.030 --> 03:35.960
Wen Chengye!

03:46.520 --> 03:47.150
Here.

03:50.150 --> 03:51.280
This belongs to you.

04:00.750 --> 04:01.480
I'm leaving.

04:05.590 --> 04:06.280
Be safe.

04:06.280 --> 04:06.810
Bye-bye.

04:10.150 --> 04:11.550
Why were you guys so fast?

04:11.750 --> 04:12.950
Where's Wen Chengye?

04:13.120 --> 04:15.840
He said he gets carsick,
so he went to take the high-speed rail.

04:15.840 --> 04:18.000
So the reason he always gave us attitude
on the bus

04:18.000 --> 04:19.870
was because he gets carsick.

04:19.870 --> 04:21.120
Should we buy some fruit

04:21.120 --> 04:22.050
and go visit him?

04:22.600 --> 04:23.560
That's so sweet.

04:23.560 --> 04:24.560
I'll let him know.

04:24.680 --> 04:25.360
No, no, no!

04:25.360 --> 04:26.270
Don't tell him it was my idea.

04:26.270 --> 04:29.470
Qin Ao said he wants to buy you some fruit
and bring it over.

04:30.240 --> 04:31.440
Why would you do that?

04:34.870 --> 04:36.390
He replied? No way.

04:36.830 --> 04:37.630
That was fast.

04:39.190 --> 04:39.950
"Idiot."

04:42.830 --> 04:44.159
-What's that supposed to mean?
-Bro.

04:44.159 --> 04:45.190
What do you think?

04:45.190 --> 04:46.480
It means he likes you, of course.

04:46.480 --> 04:48.610
Why didn't he send that to anyone else?

04:49.040 --> 04:49.510
Do you like it?

04:49.510 --> 04:50.600
If you do, I'll send it to you
every day.

04:50.600 --> 04:52.600
Sure, Mr. CEO. I accept.

04:52.600 --> 04:55.680
-Send it to me every day, alright?
-What's your problem?

04:55.680 --> 04:57.000
Looks like you guys
really aren't too tired.

04:57.000 --> 04:58.159
The bus is here. Get on.

04:58.159 --> 04:59.659
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

04:59.690 --> 05:00.830
Get on.

05:01.870 --> 05:03.750
-Let's go.
-Don't fall behind.

05:03.750 --> 05:04.190
Move faster, alright?

05:04.190 --> 05:06.000
Hurry up. It's so crowded.

05:06.950 --> 05:09.510
Next time, we'll definitely win.

06:12.830 --> 06:15.600
Sickness really does hit you
like a ton of bricks.

06:15.600 --> 06:17.240
You took so long to open the door.

06:17.240 --> 06:17.870
Let's go inside.

06:17.870 --> 06:19.130
I bought you some food.

06:25.030 --> 06:26.590
Hello, Ivory.

06:26.830 --> 06:28.040
I bought you some medicine

06:28.040 --> 06:29.570
and made you some porridge.

06:34.000 --> 06:34.800
Thank you.

06:38.720 --> 06:39.500
It's sweet?

06:39.830 --> 06:40.510
Yes.

06:40.510 --> 06:42.270
You should eat sweet porridge
when you're sick.

06:42.270 --> 06:43.270
You don't like it?

06:50.240 --> 06:51.650
How are you feeling now?

06:53.130 --> 06:54.010
I'm okay.

06:54.040 --> 06:55.480
I just still have a fever.

07:09.650 --> 07:11.200
You do have a bit of a fever.

07:11.270 --> 07:13.870
I'll go get you
some fever-reducing medicine.

07:15.010 --> 07:17.080
♪ I caught your eyes ♪

07:17.550 --> 07:19.920
♪ On the summer night ♪

07:20.400 --> 07:25.910
♪ Like stars that glow so bright ♪

07:23.390 --> 07:25.850
I don't feel like taking medicine
right now.

07:27.430 --> 07:29.690
♪ A spark in my heart ♪

07:30.400 --> 07:31.110
Lin Wanxing.

07:30.400 --> 07:36.190
♪ Lost in a dream secretly ♪

07:32.800 --> 07:33.360
I...

07:37.480 --> 07:38.390
Oh no.

07:39.690 --> 07:44.920
♪ With the evening breeze
whispering in my ear ♪

07:45.650 --> 07:51.030
♪ Fireworks bloom across the sky ♪

07:48.310 --> 07:50.240
I think I'm almost recovered.

07:50.240 --> 07:51.770
Maybe I should just go home.

07:51.870 --> 07:54.170
♪ Shimmering in your eyes ♪

07:52.720 --> 07:54.830
Feeling chills is a sign
that a fever's coming on.

07:54.830 --> 07:56.000
The medicine is on its way.

07:54.830 --> 08:00.650
♪ And spreading into
a gentle sea of stars ♪

07:56.360 --> 07:57.760
Take it before you leave.

08:03.900 --> 08:05.730
♪ Every night ♪

08:06.650 --> 08:08.620
♪ I reach for starlight ♪

08:09.520 --> 08:11.350
♪ Wandering through dreams with you ♪

08:11.920 --> 08:14.130
♪ I follow the beat of my heart ♪

08:15.300 --> 08:17.780
♪ Like dust floating in the air ♪

08:18.900 --> 08:20.700
♪ Because of your love ♪

08:20.800 --> 08:22.720
Here, have some hot water too.

08:21.590 --> 08:26.150
♪ I shine brilliantly ♪

08:37.789 --> 08:38.789
You really are burning up.

08:38.789 --> 08:40.919
You're even hotter than the hot water—

08:42.679 --> 08:44.610
but actually kind of nice and warm.

08:47.220 --> 08:49.290
♪ I caught your eyes ♪

08:49.760 --> 08:52.130
♪ On the summer night ♪

08:52.600 --> 08:58.110
♪ Like stars that glow so bright ♪

08:54.910 --> 08:57.370
How much longer
until the medicine arrives?

08:57.600 --> 08:58.460
Should be soon.

08:59.510 --> 09:01.620
♪ A spark in my heart ♪

09:02.480 --> 09:08.270
♪ Lost in a dream secretly ♪

09:04.790 --> 09:06.650
Do you feel really disappointed?

09:07.550 --> 09:08.720
You were just one goal away from winning.

09:08.720 --> 09:09.510
Let's not

09:11.120 --> 09:12.630
talk about football for now.

09:11.770 --> 09:16.970
♪ With the evening breeze
whispering in my ear ♪

09:12.720 --> 09:14.450
Then what should we talk about?

09:17.550 --> 09:19.670
Let's just keep each other warm
as fellow patients.

09:17.730 --> 09:23.100
♪ Fireworks bloom across the sky ♪

09:20.320 --> 09:22.840
Everything else can wait
until we get better.

09:22.840 --> 09:24.150
Is this really mutual?

09:23.950 --> 09:26.250
♪ Shimmering in your eyes ♪

09:24.150 --> 09:25.720
Your temperature's so much higher
than mine.

09:25.720 --> 09:27.790
You're just transferring heat to me
one-way.

09:26.770 --> 09:32.590
♪ And spreading into
a gentle sea of stars ♪

09:29.630 --> 09:32.230
Okay,
Your Highness, the Shining Star Genius.

09:32.430 --> 09:34.720
So, are you going to pay me
a "one-way heat transfer fee"?

09:34.720 --> 09:36.240
Why should I pay you?

09:35.840 --> 09:37.670
♪ Every night ♪

09:36.240 --> 09:37.690
You're the one
who pulled me into your arms.

09:37.690 --> 09:40.050
Besides, you're probably the one
who passed this illness on to me, right?

09:38.590 --> 09:40.560
♪ I reach for starlight ♪

09:41.460 --> 09:43.290
♪ Wandering through dreams with you ♪

09:43.860 --> 09:46.080
♪ I follow the beat of my heart ♪

09:47.240 --> 09:49.690
♪ Like dust floating in the air ♪

09:50.840 --> 09:52.490
♪ Because of your love ♪

09:54.600 --> 09:55.330
Wen Chengye!

09:57.360 --> 09:58.150
Wen Chengye!

09:59.240 --> 10:00.300
What are you doing?

10:01.240 --> 10:03.360
You've really gotten too big
for your boots, huh?

10:03.360 --> 10:05.200
You actually dared to sneak off
and play football again!

10:05.200 --> 10:06.630
I'm not only going to
keep playing football.

10:06.630 --> 10:07.910
I'm also staying at Hongjing Team.

10:07.910 --> 10:09.120
I told you,

10:09.840 --> 10:11.720
you have to do as you're told.

10:12.150 --> 10:13.150
What are you trying to do?

10:13.150 --> 10:14.750
I don't get a say here, right?

10:14.790 --> 10:15.860
Then I'm going somewhere
where I have a say.

10:15.860 --> 10:16.790
Well, look at you.

10:16.790 --> 10:18.720
You've got the nerve
to talk back to me now,

10:18.720 --> 10:19.240
huh?

10:21.630 --> 10:22.360
Get in there!

10:27.030 --> 10:27.970
Wen Ruigang!

10:28.200 --> 10:29.840
Unless you lock me up here
for the rest of my life,

10:29.840 --> 10:31.270
I'm still going to play football
once I get out!

10:31.270 --> 10:32.870
I'll be honest with you, too!

10:33.510 --> 10:34.510
The Parents' Committee is currently

10:34.510 --> 10:35.320
extremely dissatisfied

10:35.320 --> 10:36.720
with your football team!

10:37.390 --> 10:39.390
If I were to give it even a little push,

10:39.390 --> 10:42.190
the football team
would definitely be disbanded.

10:42.550 --> 10:44.200
If you want your football team

10:44.200 --> 10:45.460
to disappear for good,

10:45.790 --> 10:46.750
then keep going.

10:47.150 --> 10:48.150
Please, go ahead.

10:57.720 --> 10:59.120
Reflect on your actions!

11:39.860 --> 11:42.640
[Replay Footage] [Video]

11:49.030 --> 11:51.060
[Yongchuan Provincial Youth Super League]

11:49.150 --> 11:50.390
Ms. Lin, refresh it again.

11:50.390 --> 11:51.440
Refresh it again.

11:51.440 --> 11:53.270
-The school's network's so bad.
-What kind of network is this?

11:53.270 --> 11:54.150
-Refresh it again.
-Exactly.

11:54.150 --> 11:56.320
-It's stuck here.
-The network's so bad.

11:55.060 --> 11:58.100
[Yongchuan Provincial Youth Super League]

11:56.320 --> 11:58.510
-Refresh it again. Refresh it.
-Come on.

11:58.510 --> 11:59.600
The network's lagging.

11:59.600 --> 12:01.030
-We need to refresh it.
-What's going on?

12:01.030 --> 12:02.890
-Let's refresh it again.
-Quiet!

12:03.670 --> 12:05.720
I'm only just recovered.

12:05.720 --> 12:07.670
If you keep yelling like this,
I'll get sick all over again.

12:07.670 --> 12:09.270
You might not be anxious, but I am.

12:09.270 --> 12:10.390
Yeah. Exactly.

12:10.390 --> 12:11.270
Try refreshing it again.

12:11.270 --> 12:12.390
R-Refresh it.

12:11.410 --> 12:14.460
[Group B Stage 2 Standings
(As of Round 4)]

12:14.540 --> 12:16.930
[Yongchuan Hengjiu] [Chuncheng Xinpeng]
[Shenhai Yinbo] [Hongjing No. 8 High]

12:17.510 --> 12:18.750
1-1!

12:19.600 --> 12:21.640
We've advanced to the next round!

12:22.440 --> 12:24.390
It was a 1–1 draw!

12:24.390 --> 12:27.150
-So? What does this mean?
-It was a draw!

12:27.150 --> 12:29.080
Did you even finish
elementary school math?

12:29.080 --> 12:30.030
As long as Yongchuan wins all their games

12:30.030 --> 12:32.120
and we beat Shenhai, we can advance!

12:35.670 --> 12:38.750
-We finally have a chance to get revenge!
-That's right!

12:38.750 --> 12:39.550
Where's Wen Chengye?

12:39.550 --> 12:41.030
-Right.
-W-Wen Chengye?

12:41.320 --> 12:42.650
Did you see Wen Chengye?

12:43.270 --> 12:44.840
I haven't seen him all day.

12:45.080 --> 12:45.910
Maybe he asked for a leave.

12:45.910 --> 12:47.790
-I was just guessing.
-Wen Chengye.

12:47.790 --> 12:48.870
Ms. Lin.

12:49.000 --> 12:50.140
-Hello, Director.
-Director Qian.

12:50.140 --> 12:50.630
Director Qian.

12:50.630 --> 12:51.440
You're all here.

12:51.440 --> 12:53.030
Director Qian, we've made it
to the qualification round.

12:53.030 --> 12:53.710
-That's right.
-Yeah.

12:53.710 --> 12:55.030
-I know. I know.
-We drew 1–1!

12:55.030 --> 12:57.030
Congratulations. Congratulations.

12:57.030 --> 12:59.240
Director Qian, is there something wrong?

12:59.240 --> 13:00.630
While we're celebrating,

13:00.630 --> 13:02.030
I also have an important announcement

13:02.030 --> 13:03.030
to make to all of you.

13:03.030 --> 13:03.640
-Okay.
-Okay.

13:03.640 --> 13:04.390
W-What is it?

13:04.910 --> 13:06.570
Well, Wen Chengye has decided

13:07.510 --> 13:09.550
not to continue with the football team.

13:09.550 --> 13:10.780
Are you kidding?

13:11.030 --> 13:13.720
He also doesn't plan to
continue his studies in China

13:13.720 --> 13:15.550
for the second half of his senior year.

13:15.550 --> 13:16.960
Not studying in China?

13:16.960 --> 13:19.600
Does that mean he's going abroad
for a foundation program?

13:19.600 --> 13:20.460
Yes.

13:21.150 --> 13:21.870
Director Qian,

13:21.870 --> 13:23.620
is this Wen Chengye's own decision,

13:23.620 --> 13:25.690
or are his parents against it?

13:25.840 --> 13:27.150
I can try talking to them.

13:27.150 --> 13:30.950
His parents have explicitly stated
they do not wish to be disturbed.

13:31.510 --> 13:32.390
Ms. Lin.

13:32.790 --> 13:33.480
I know

13:33.910 --> 13:36.170
you want to respect the students' wishes

13:36.510 --> 13:38.700
and keep the football team

13:38.790 --> 13:40.550
as intact as possible.

13:42.150 --> 13:43.840
But in this matter,

13:44.750 --> 13:46.610
there's really nothing we can do.

13:48.260 --> 13:48.920
That's all.

13:49.320 --> 13:50.380
You guys continue.

13:58.270 --> 13:59.390
Don't worry, everyone.

13:59.390 --> 14:00.920
I'll figure something out.

14:27.840 --> 14:29.500
Do you always walk so quietly?

14:31.630 --> 14:33.960
You were just too deep in thought,
Ms. Lin.

14:35.440 --> 14:37.030
But if you get sick again,

14:37.750 --> 14:41.080
there'll be no one to transfer heat
to you one-way this time.

14:45.750 --> 14:48.150
I just received a notice
from Director Qian

14:48.550 --> 14:50.680
that Wen Chengye is quitting the team,

14:51.030 --> 14:53.030
and that he's going to study abroad.

14:56.630 --> 14:57.360
I know

14:58.550 --> 15:00.480
he probably doesn't want to leave.

15:01.000 --> 15:03.200
It must've been his family's decision.

15:03.240 --> 15:04.720
And even as his teacher,

15:05.630 --> 15:07.480
I shouldn't interfere too much.

15:08.600 --> 15:09.930
I'm trying to figure out

15:10.870 --> 15:12.140
how I can help him.

15:15.080 --> 15:15.880
Don't forget.

15:17.360 --> 15:18.440
He's not alone.

15:23.200 --> 15:24.390
And with a strong-willed child

15:24.390 --> 15:25.790
like Wen Chengye,

15:26.670 --> 15:27.630
what we need to do

15:28.030 --> 15:29.390
is be fully prepared

15:30.240 --> 15:31.430
and give him a helping hand

15:31.430 --> 15:32.390
when necessary.

15:42.530 --> 15:45.870
[Wen Chengye]

15:52.910 --> 15:54.390
Wen Chengye sent me a video.

15:54.390 --> 15:55.150
Wen Chengye!

15:57.510 --> 15:58.570
What are you doing?

16:01.270 --> 16:02.750
You actually dared to sneak off
and play football again!

16:02.750 --> 16:04.000
I'm not only going to
keep playing football.

16:04.000 --> 16:05.270
I'm also staying at Hongjing Team.

16:05.270 --> 16:07.150
I have told you many times.

16:07.150 --> 16:09.240
You don't call the shots in this family!

16:09.240 --> 16:10.200
Well, look at you.

16:10.200 --> 16:12.320
You've got the nerve
to talk back to me now, huh?

16:12.020 --> 16:16.220
[Wen Chengye]

16:12.790 --> 16:14.120
I recorded this secretly.

16:14.120 --> 16:15.960
Ms. Lin, do me a favor.

16:30.240 --> 16:31.480
This is the study abroad contract

16:31.480 --> 16:33.440
and the application
to withdraw from the team.

16:33.440 --> 16:35.200
Once you've thought it through,

16:35.200 --> 16:35.840
sign it.

16:42.510 --> 16:42.960
Hello.

16:44.390 --> 16:45.950
Principal Zhang, hello.

16:46.600 --> 16:49.130
I am Wen Ruigang
from the Parents' Committee.

16:50.550 --> 16:52.240
Regarding what we discussed this morning,

16:52.240 --> 16:54.200
about disbanding the football team,

16:54.200 --> 16:56.360
I've thought about it carefully.

16:56.750 --> 16:58.750
Here's what I think. I think...

17:01.550 --> 17:02.200
Pardon me,

17:02.200 --> 17:02.960
Principal Zhang.

17:02.960 --> 17:04.310
I need to take an important call.

17:04.310 --> 17:05.390
Can I call you back later?

17:05.390 --> 17:06.500
Sorry about that.

17:10.069 --> 17:11.200
You've come around?

17:14.510 --> 17:15.240
I'll sign it.

17:17.500 --> 17:19.020
You could've saved us all this trouble.

17:19.020 --> 17:20.609
[Application for Withdrawal
from the Football Team]

17:27.750 --> 17:28.280
[Applicant] [Legal Guardian: Wen Ruigang]

17:30.070 --> 17:30.600
Alright.

17:31.000 --> 17:31.960
Go upstairs first.

17:31.960 --> 17:33.220
Sign these two copies,

17:33.350 --> 17:34.810
and put them in my bedroom.

17:34.960 --> 17:35.820
Did you hear me?

17:36.270 --> 17:36.750
Go on.

17:48.720 --> 17:49.510
Who are you guys?

17:49.510 --> 17:50.680
Hello, Mr. Wen.

17:50.680 --> 17:51.880
I'm a teacher at No. 8 High School

17:51.880 --> 17:54.400
and the supervisor of
the school football team, Ms. Lin.

17:54.400 --> 17:56.350
I'm the team coach, Wang Fa.

17:57.640 --> 17:59.550
We're here to see Chengye

17:59.550 --> 18:03.110
and talk to him about some matters
concerning the football team.

18:03.110 --> 18:03.920
I'm sorry.

18:04.400 --> 18:07.000
Wen Chengye is leaving
the football team soon.

18:07.960 --> 18:08.680
It wouldn't be appropriate for him
to see you.

18:08.680 --> 18:09.640
Hold on a second.

18:17.160 --> 18:19.660
Mr. Wen, is Chengye home?

18:33.480 --> 18:34.240
He's sick

18:34.240 --> 18:35.220
and resting at home.

18:35.220 --> 18:37.110
I've already asked for leave for him.

18:37.110 --> 18:39.640
If you have something to say,
please go ahe...

18:41.030 --> 18:41.920
I'm not sick!

18:42.270 --> 18:43.680
Who allowed you to come down? Go upstairs!

18:43.680 --> 18:44.590
Mr. Wen.

18:44.590 --> 18:45.270
Excuse me.

18:45.590 --> 18:46.960
I'm disciplining my own child,

18:46.960 --> 18:48.440
and I don't need anyone else to interfere.

18:48.440 --> 18:49.070
Is that so?

18:49.350 --> 18:50.310
Slapping me,

18:50.590 --> 18:51.440
insulting me,

18:51.880 --> 18:54.310
not letting me eat, locking me up
in a dark room—

18:54.310 --> 18:55.830
is that discipline or abuse?

18:55.830 --> 18:57.000
Stop spouting nonsense.

18:57.000 --> 18:58.440
You've got no right to speak here.
Go upstairs.

18:58.440 --> 18:59.270
I'm the person involved.

18:59.270 --> 19:01.200
How do I not have the right to speak?

19:04.510 --> 19:05.620
Wen Chengye.

19:06.400 --> 19:07.680
I'm sending you abroad

19:07.880 --> 19:09.200
so you can receive an elite education

19:09.200 --> 19:10.160
and have a bright future,

19:10.160 --> 19:11.690
and this is how you repay me?

19:11.790 --> 19:14.120
You really don't know what's good for you.

19:16.750 --> 19:17.950
I've told you before.

19:18.880 --> 19:19.510
First,

19:20.110 --> 19:21.480
I can study abroad,

19:21.480 --> 19:22.310
but not now,

19:22.310 --> 19:24.270
and I definitely won't go to
a business school!

19:24.270 --> 19:25.880
I know what I want to study.

19:27.000 --> 19:27.640
Second,

19:29.310 --> 19:30.240
as for football,

19:31.070 --> 19:32.430
I'll keep playing it.

19:36.680 --> 19:38.640
If you don't follow the path
I arranged for you,

19:38.640 --> 19:40.440
you won't get into a good school.

19:40.640 --> 19:41.030
Also,

19:41.750 --> 19:43.440
if you keep playing this stupid football

19:43.440 --> 19:44.680
and it ends up affecting your application,

19:44.680 --> 19:47.210
who's going to take responsibility
for that?

19:48.800 --> 19:49.600
Mr. Wen.

19:50.440 --> 19:52.460
Football is not a bad thing

19:52.490 --> 19:53.850
for Chengye.

19:55.750 --> 19:58.110
Wen Chengye's a very talented
football player.

19:58.110 --> 19:59.200
As far as I know,

19:59.720 --> 20:01.180
U.S. admissions officers

20:01.270 --> 20:02.870
don't only consider grades.

20:03.030 --> 20:04.500
Football could actually be

20:04.500 --> 20:05.890
an advantage for him.

20:05.910 --> 20:07.440
You are just an ordinary school team,

20:07.440 --> 20:08.880
not even a professional club.

20:08.880 --> 20:12.240
How could playing football there
lead to any meaningful achievements?

20:12.240 --> 20:12.960
Mr. Wen.

20:13.640 --> 20:16.480
Our team is currently competing
in the Youth Super League.

20:16.480 --> 20:18.080
Wen Chengye plays very well,

20:18.400 --> 20:20.440
and he has what it takes
to compete against professional teams.

20:20.440 --> 20:21.400
If we keep playing,

20:21.400 --> 20:22.860
we might get good results.

20:22.960 --> 20:23.550
Besides,

20:24.440 --> 20:26.270
I can write a recommendation letter
for Wen Chengye.

20:26.270 --> 20:27.310
What's the use of

20:28.630 --> 20:29.590
you writing a recommendation letter?

20:29.590 --> 20:30.590
My name is Wang Fa.

20:30.750 --> 20:32.610
I'm a former coach of Nanton Club.

20:33.110 --> 20:34.910
You can look up my resume online.

20:34.920 --> 20:37.790
You said you're a former coach
of Nanton Club.

20:38.880 --> 20:39.640
So what?

20:40.200 --> 20:40.920
What practical benefits

20:40.920 --> 20:42.720
can you actually bring to my son?

20:42.790 --> 20:43.640
I don't need it.

20:43.640 --> 20:45.200
Who else wouldn't cherish

20:45.200 --> 20:46.000
the resources you have?

20:46.000 --> 20:47.510
Did I ask for any of those?

20:47.510 --> 20:49.360
You have no place in this house!

20:50.790 --> 20:52.650
I have many more videos like this.

20:53.720 --> 20:55.030
I'm your only son.

20:55.590 --> 20:57.440
If I sue you for abuse

20:57.880 --> 20:58.810
with this video,

20:59.510 --> 21:00.440
what do you think

21:00.440 --> 21:02.700
it would do to the company's stock price?

21:05.550 --> 21:06.590
Where did you get this video?

21:06.590 --> 21:08.240
And the one on your teacher's phone.

21:08.240 --> 21:09.840
I installed cameras at home.

21:10.640 --> 21:11.510
You really are...

21:11.510 --> 21:12.400
Mr. Wen, don't get violent.

21:12.400 --> 21:13.440
You really think you can make it

21:13.440 --> 21:14.720
on your own without me?

21:14.720 --> 21:15.480
Wen Chengye!

21:23.160 --> 21:23.680
Dad,

21:27.720 --> 21:28.920
I want to give it a try.

21:30.200 --> 21:31.800
I really want to give it a try.

21:46.440 --> 21:47.440
Mr. Wen.

21:48.200 --> 21:49.640
We totally understand

21:49.640 --> 21:51.220
your good intentions.

21:51.720 --> 21:52.640
We know

21:52.640 --> 21:55.680
you're doing this because
you hope he can have a better future.

21:55.680 --> 21:56.960
But as you can see,

21:56.960 --> 21:58.760
Wen Chengye is very determined.

22:02.960 --> 22:05.790
Children are never
the property of their parents.

22:06.480 --> 22:08.400
They should have the right

22:08.640 --> 22:10.370
to choose their own life goals.

22:11.200 --> 22:13.030
As teachers and parents,

22:13.680 --> 22:15.010
we should respect them.

22:23.790 --> 22:24.400
Fine.

22:27.400 --> 22:28.930
If you want to be a stray dog,

22:30.160 --> 22:31.020
suit yourself.

22:31.400 --> 22:32.130
Wen Cheng...

22:32.920 --> 22:34.320
We're here to save you...

22:36.460 --> 22:37.590
Coach. Ms. Lin.

22:37.590 --> 22:38.720
Why are you here too?

22:38.790 --> 22:39.200
You...

22:39.550 --> 22:40.750
Why are you guys here?

22:41.920 --> 22:43.750
You haven't been to school.

22:43.750 --> 22:45.000
We've been worried sick about you,

22:45.000 --> 22:46.400
so we came to check on you.

22:48.160 --> 22:50.270
Ms. Lin and Coach were really quick
to take action.

22:50.270 --> 22:52.930
It almost makes us feel like
we came for nothing.

22:56.680 --> 22:57.580
Not at all.

22:59.050 --> 23:01.050
At least you made quite an entrance.

23:06.310 --> 23:07.160
Please

23:08.440 --> 23:09.310
leave my house.

23:09.920 --> 23:10.270
Dad.

23:13.920 --> 23:14.980
I'm not a stray dog.

23:15.550 --> 23:16.550
I've got friends.

23:35.640 --> 23:36.960
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

23:36.960 --> 23:39.420
You're welcome.
We didn't help much anyway.

23:39.790 --> 23:41.240
Coach, don't forget about
the recommendation letter.

23:41.240 --> 23:43.100
Let's go have some clams and beer.

23:43.200 --> 23:44.590
Coach, Ms. Lin.

23:45.200 --> 23:46.240
This bicycle

23:46.240 --> 23:47.240
is mine.

23:47.640 --> 23:48.970
I'll let you two have it.

23:49.110 --> 23:51.960
Riding my beloved bicycle...

23:52.720 --> 23:54.030
I'll just take a taxi.

23:54.050 --> 23:55.070
Hop on.

23:55.550 --> 23:56.680
I'll give you a ride.

23:58.400 --> 23:59.600
Did I hear that right?

23:59.830 --> 24:00.790
Get on. Get on.

24:00.790 --> 24:03.020
What's wrong with you? Don't block my way.

24:03.020 --> 24:03.820
Alright then.

24:04.030 --> 24:04.490
Thanks.

24:04.680 --> 24:05.380
Slow down.

24:05.550 --> 24:06.680
I'm off.

24:08.760 --> 24:09.590
Slow down.

24:09.590 --> 24:10.600
Boss, slow down.

24:11.000 --> 24:11.790
Lu,

24:11.960 --> 24:13.110
have you gained weight again?

24:13.110 --> 24:15.710
Move it, guys in front!
Don't hold everyone up.

24:47.440 --> 24:48.110
Ms. Lin,

24:49.400 --> 24:58.050
[Isn't it obvious? I play football to win.
— Qin Ao]

24:49.680 --> 24:51.340
here's the homework I owe you.

24:51.750 --> 24:54.240
You asked me why I play football.

24:55.680 --> 24:56.830
I'd say it's simple—

24:56.830 --> 24:57.720
I play to win.

24:58.360 --> 25:00.020
It's a handsome photo of mine.

25:07.040 --> 25:09.130
[Isn't it obvious? I play football to win.
— Qin Ao]

25:15.880 --> 25:17.110
This is my homework.

25:17.110 --> 25:19.680
I drew every moment from our match.

25:19.280 --> 25:22.200
[Could victory really slip away
like this?]

25:21.200 --> 25:22.270
The whistle blew,

25:22.270 --> 25:23.640
cutting through the clear sky,

25:23.640 --> 25:24.720
and the game began.

25:24.720 --> 25:25.920
Every pass we made

25:25.920 --> 25:27.640
was aimed toward the same goal:

25:27.640 --> 25:28.270
victory.

25:29.590 --> 25:30.560
Ms. Lin.

25:30.640 --> 25:32.640
I thought about this question
for a long time,

25:32.640 --> 25:34.440
and in the end I came to a conclusion:

25:34.440 --> 25:37.110
football without victory is nothing.

25:35.720 --> 25:38.270
[Now I'm ready to win.]

25:37.640 --> 25:40.960
So I think football is all about winning.

25:39.630 --> 25:45.310
♪ Waiting for a dark cloud
to pass by you ♪

25:42.400 --> 25:43.350
Ms. Lin.

25:43.350 --> 25:44.590
Actually, I've spent a long time

25:44.410 --> 25:45.620
[Victory is never achieved by chance.
Next time]

25:44.590 --> 25:45.720
thinking about this question.

25:45.640 --> 25:47.300
[the referee blows the whistle,]

25:45.720 --> 25:47.920
But football isn't a math problem,

25:45.910 --> 25:50.720
♪ Listen closely to its cries ♪

25:47.330 --> 25:49.210
[I'll make sure I run faster
than I did last time.]

25:47.920 --> 25:49.400
so I don't know if there's a right answer.

25:49.400 --> 25:50.160
No matter what,

25:50.160 --> 25:52.090
I don't want to lose the next match.

25:52.510 --> 25:57.770
♪ The heavy rain will wash away
your reflection ♪

25:54.200 --> 25:55.270
Ms. Lin.

25:55.550 --> 25:58.790
I think we should play football
with a winning smile.

25:58.440 --> 26:03.940
♪ And carry it toward distant scenery ♪

25:58.820 --> 26:03.090
[Next time I score, I'll flash a V sign
at the camera.]

25:59.030 --> 26:00.240
We should give everything we have

26:00.240 --> 26:02.440
and leave every drop of our sweat
on our pitch.

26:02.440 --> 26:03.590
Just wait and see—

26:03.590 --> 26:05.880
the smiles and victories that belong to us
are coming.

26:05.440 --> 26:11.300
♪ Every experience has its meaning ♪

26:05.880 --> 26:08.410
We'll prove to the whole world
that we can win.

26:08.880 --> 26:09.830
Ms. Lin.

26:09.830 --> 26:12.110
I think football is about the feeling of

26:11.890 --> 26:16.690
♪ Scene by scene, they come together
to form who I am ♪

26:12.440 --> 26:14.550
the 11 of us playing together.

26:14.550 --> 26:16.720
Every time we win,

26:16.720 --> 26:18.920
when all 11 of us celebrate

26:18.360 --> 26:23.510
♪ Even the wounds
that leave behind their marks ♪

26:18.920 --> 26:19.880
and share that excitement together,

26:19.880 --> 26:21.960
I feel like there's no better feeling
than that.

26:21.960 --> 26:23.480
If there's a next time,

26:23.640 --> 26:26.350
I'll definitely turn that
"what if I had scored"

26:24.490 --> 26:29.660
♪ Have taught me how to heal myself ♪

26:26.350 --> 26:29.070
into "I did it this time, but missed."

26:29.450 --> 26:30.140
[I want to win, not to prove anything,]

26:29.880 --> 26:32.880
Ms. Lin, I posted a poll on the forum

26:30.170 --> 26:31.030
[but because I know I have to hold
this last line of defense.]

26:30.510 --> 26:36.470
♪ The love I have given,
the love I have received ♪

26:32.880 --> 26:33.880
to ask if football

26:33.880 --> 26:35.400
is really all about winning.

26:34.550 --> 26:35.100
[I don't agree.
Are Messi and Maradona's greatness]

26:35.130 --> 26:35.450
[really defined by the number of trophies
they've won?]

26:35.470 --> 26:35.780
[It's about their artistry.]

26:35.750 --> 26:36.880
It sparked a lot of comments.

26:36.190 --> 26:36.510
[In a 90-minute match,
every single moment]

26:36.530 --> 26:36.920
[is a joy to watch.
The result isn't what matters.]

26:36.880 --> 26:38.000
Some said it is,

26:36.940 --> 26:37.240
[What matters is the process,
and the teammates who stand beside you.]

26:37.120 --> 26:42.890
♪ Every one of them gives me the strength
not to fear being hurt ♪

26:38.000 --> 26:39.510
while others said it's not.

26:38.120 --> 26:38.420
[With such a strong desire to win,
why don't you go play football yourself?]

26:39.510 --> 26:40.960
But to me,

26:41.510 --> 26:43.570
I don't want to leave any regrets
in the next match.

26:43.570 --> 26:49.180
♪ Let my tears be carried away,
back into the ocean ♪

26:44.270 --> 26:47.790
Ms. Lin, when I got back,
I immediately cast a divination.

26:47.790 --> 26:48.960
He did it again.

26:48.960 --> 26:50.110
And

26:50.030 --> 26:55.270
♪ And blown toward flowers
blooming far away ♪

26:50.110 --> 26:51.960
according to the hexagram,

26:51.960 --> 26:54.480
I got the Tai hexagram.

26:53.190 --> 26:59.330
[Zhi Hui]

26:54.480 --> 26:57.200
Whether from the imagery
of the Tai hexagram

26:56.580 --> 27:01.910
♪ I fill the blank spaces of life
with colors ♪

26:57.200 --> 26:59.550
or the philosophy
contained in its judgment,

26:59.550 --> 27:01.350
they both reveal the same truth:

27:01.480 --> 27:05.270
football, by its very nature,
exists for the pursuit of victory.

27:02.650 --> 27:08.390
♪ My dreams are not afraid to awaken;
they continue to exist ♪

27:06.000 --> 27:06.880
Ms. Lin.

27:07.310 --> 27:08.270
I've sent you the video

27:08.270 --> 27:09.750
that I edited.

27:09.170 --> 27:15.230
♪ I go beyond the dark clouds
and feel the haze disperse ♪

27:09.750 --> 27:10.950
Remember to watch it.

27:11.310 --> 27:12.240
To sum up,

27:12.240 --> 27:14.200
I play football for 3 goals:

27:14.440 --> 27:16.030
victory, victory,

27:15.830 --> 27:21.530
♪ Let me understand myself more clearly ♪

27:16.030 --> 27:17.000
and victory.

27:17.000 --> 27:17.800
That's right.

27:21.070 --> 27:21.790
Ms. Lin.

27:22.160 --> 27:23.760
Scoring goals is my destiny.

27:24.790 --> 27:25.680
Ms. Lin.

27:26.590 --> 27:27.960
As for the assignment you gave us,

27:27.960 --> 27:30.360
I actually thought about it
for a long time.

27:31.440 --> 27:32.110
As you know,

27:32.110 --> 27:33.550
I'm not very good with words.

27:33.550 --> 27:34.240
So

27:34.480 --> 27:37.680
I decided to express my thoughts
through a video instead.

27:38.000 --> 27:40.270
Football is all about winning.

27:39.980 --> 27:45.390
♪ Every experience has its meaning ♪

27:41.720 --> 27:42.880
Louder.

27:42.880 --> 27:45.720
Football is all about winning!

27:45.720 --> 27:49.400
Football is all about winning!

27:46.320 --> 27:50.800
♪ Scene by scene, they come together
to form who I am ♪

27:52.090 --> 27:57.850
♪ Even the wounds
that leave behind their marks ♪

27:57.870 --> 28:05.270
♪ Have taught me how to heal myself ♪

28:08.330 --> 28:13.480
♪ The love I have given,
the love I have received ♪

28:14.750 --> 28:15.660
♪ Every single one ♪

28:15.960 --> 28:17.270
Bend your right knee.

28:17.270 --> 28:18.640
Lock the hammock
with the back of your knee.

28:18.640 --> 28:19.750
Extend your left leg

28:19.750 --> 28:20.960
straight down toward the floor.

28:20.960 --> 28:22.240
Release your hands

28:22.240 --> 28:23.790
and fly backwards.

28:24.400 --> 28:26.000
Open up your chest

28:26.000 --> 28:27.680
and gaze toward the floor.

28:28.200 --> 28:28.680
Three.

28:29.510 --> 28:31.240
Straighten your left leg. Two.

28:32.510 --> 28:33.030
One.

28:33.030 --> 28:34.640
Good. Now lift your head,
engage your core,

28:34.640 --> 28:36.030
and hold the hammock at your hips
with both hands.

28:36.030 --> 28:36.790
Right leg out.

28:36.790 --> 28:37.920
Reach both hands up.

28:38.200 --> 28:40.550
Right leg forward, left leg back.

28:41.030 --> 28:42.480
Lean backwards.

29:08.070 --> 29:08.960
It really hurts.

29:08.960 --> 29:10.090
My back is breaking.

29:16.340 --> 29:17.600
You did great just now.

29:17.790 --> 29:18.880
So, what do you think?

29:18.880 --> 29:20.410
Want to continue next week?

29:20.640 --> 29:21.790
Alright, alright.

29:29.200 --> 29:31.160
Hello, Chairman Wang.

29:31.590 --> 29:33.750
I'm at the Anda Hotel now.

29:33.750 --> 29:35.830
Why did you go to the rival's hotel
for no reason?

29:35.830 --> 29:37.200
Come over here.

29:38.440 --> 29:40.640
Hello? My signal is bad.

29:41.240 --> 29:44.000
-Hello?
-Hello? Hello?

29:48.590 --> 29:50.450
He'll definitely call me in a bit.

29:51.000 --> 29:51.720
See?

29:56.960 --> 29:58.000
Hello, Chairman.

29:58.590 --> 30:00.110
Are you with Wang Tian?

30:01.960 --> 30:03.590
Yes, I'm with Wang Tian.

30:04.720 --> 30:06.000
Then why is your signal good

30:06.000 --> 30:07.000
but hers was bad?

30:07.000 --> 30:08.530
Was she doing it on purpose?

30:08.920 --> 30:10.270
My signal is bad too.

30:10.510 --> 30:11.550
Very bad.

30:13.200 --> 30:13.960
Really?

30:15.070 --> 30:16.030
Yeah.

30:16.400 --> 30:18.440
Wang Tian works really hard every day.

30:18.440 --> 30:20.720
She came all the way to this remote
mountain area just to inspect the hotel.

30:20.720 --> 30:21.350
By herself.

30:21.350 --> 30:23.080
Listen if you don't believe me.

30:25.030 --> 30:26.350
So dangerous, huh?

30:27.200 --> 30:28.600
Since it's so dangerous,

30:28.650 --> 30:29.480
just leave it

30:29.510 --> 30:31.480
t-to the assistant, you two,

30:31.720 --> 30:33.270
and then come to

30:33.270 --> 30:34.510
Anda Hotel on Hu'an Road.

30:34.510 --> 30:35.750
I'll wait for you here.

30:35.750 --> 30:37.400
But we're pretty far away.

30:38.270 --> 30:40.000
I don't care if you're on Mount Huaguo

30:40.000 --> 30:41.440
or in the Water Curtain Cave,

30:41.440 --> 30:43.110
get here within 2 hours.

30:43.110 --> 30:45.110
If I don't see you by then,
you can forget about marrying into

30:45.110 --> 30:46.880
the Wang family
and becoming the live-in son-in-law.

30:46.880 --> 30:47.540
No, wait...

30:49.480 --> 30:50.280
I'm not going.

30:51.110 --> 30:51.880
If you don't go,

30:51.880 --> 30:53.640
I'll buy you 999 roses

30:53.640 --> 30:54.880
and confess my love to you
in front of everyone

30:54.880 --> 30:56.510
downstairs at the company.

31:03.830 --> 31:05.880
Anyway, I say what I mean
and I do what I say.

31:05.880 --> 31:08.140
I don't care about embarrassing myself.

31:16.440 --> 31:18.030
Uncle, we're here.

31:18.960 --> 31:20.590
You came pretty fast.

31:21.240 --> 31:22.200
Hey, sweetie, you...

31:22.200 --> 31:23.720
Wearing sunglasses indoors,

31:23.720 --> 31:25.160
are you too ashamed to show your face
or something?

31:25.160 --> 31:26.440
I like it. Leave me alone.

31:26.440 --> 31:28.270
If I had really left you alone,
would you have grown up this far?

31:28.270 --> 31:29.400
When there's a battle to fight,

31:29.400 --> 31:30.800
family sticks together.

31:31.880 --> 31:33.810
Their pastries are pretty unique.

31:34.070 --> 31:34.920
The designs are creative,

31:34.920 --> 31:36.160
and even the names
are strange and playful.

31:36.160 --> 31:37.000
It's really fun.

31:37.000 --> 31:37.880
I guess customers nowadays

31:37.880 --> 31:39.480
are really into this kind of style.

31:39.480 --> 31:40.240
Wang.

31:40.680 --> 31:42.640
Can you stop being so headstrong?

31:43.270 --> 31:45.200
You went ahead and invited someone over
without even asking me.

31:45.200 --> 31:46.200
I've already

31:46.200 --> 31:48.160
planned out my schedule.

31:48.160 --> 31:48.680
Anyway,

31:48.680 --> 31:49.960
I bought all of

31:49.960 --> 31:51.350
their best-selling items.

31:51.350 --> 31:53.000
When you're back,
call a company meeting

31:53.000 --> 31:54.680
and have the planning team study

31:54.680 --> 31:55.750
how they do it.

31:56.590 --> 31:58.030
Oh, by the way,

31:58.030 --> 31:59.750
stop calling me Wang.

31:59.750 --> 32:02.880
It doesn't sound nice.
I'm not some random guy next door.

32:03.400 --> 32:04.160
Try this.

32:04.680 --> 32:06.000
"Persimmon Wishes."

32:06.000 --> 32:06.920
Try this.

32:09.160 --> 32:10.030
Come on. Try it.

32:10.790 --> 32:12.270
Well.. I'll eat it.

32:12.270 --> 32:14.130
I... I like eating this. I like it.

32:19.200 --> 32:20.070
Delicious.

32:20.310 --> 32:21.640
It's really delicious.

32:21.880 --> 32:22.880
What do you mean?

32:23.350 --> 32:25.350
Our competitor's stuff is delicious, huh?

32:25.350 --> 32:28.210
But i-it's really p-pretty good
as a matter of fact.

32:29.200 --> 32:29.730
Sweetie.

32:30.160 --> 32:31.440
The bookstore over there
is very interesting.

32:31.440 --> 32:32.640
Take a look, alright?

32:33.000 --> 32:34.600
Come on, let's go take a look.

32:35.110 --> 32:35.920
Let's go.

32:36.440 --> 32:37.920
Alright. Let's go.

32:44.590 --> 32:45.400
See that?

32:46.030 --> 32:49.200
-This is what they call...
-The immersive atmosphere.

32:49.200 --> 32:50.260
Right, immersive.

32:50.480 --> 32:51.510
But these chairs are no good.

32:51.510 --> 32:54.110
They're too hard. It's uncomfortable
to sit on them for a long time.

32:54.110 --> 32:54.640
Uncle.

32:54.640 --> 32:57.110
Our hotel will definitely take what's good
and discard the shortcomings.

32:57.110 --> 32:57.680
You.

32:58.030 --> 32:58.920
Watch your wording.

32:58.920 --> 33:00.180
What do you mean "our"?

33:01.240 --> 33:03.510
Exactly. Don't act like we are family.

33:04.310 --> 33:05.480
Hey, Uncle, you promised me.

33:05.480 --> 33:06.960
How could you just forget it?

33:06.960 --> 33:09.090
Promised what? What did I promise you?

33:09.440 --> 33:10.830
No loud noises in public.

33:10.830 --> 33:11.890
Mind your manners.

33:12.400 --> 33:13.200
Your manners.

33:14.000 --> 33:14.590
Wang.

33:15.200 --> 33:17.270
If you want to build
a garden-themed immersive hotel,

33:17.270 --> 33:19.110
I can gather some materials for you.

33:19.110 --> 33:20.510
Sweetie, what kind of material

33:20.510 --> 33:22.270
could be more important
than firsthand experience?

33:22.270 --> 33:23.240
You young people

33:23.240 --> 33:25.290
just rely too much on high-tech.

33:25.720 --> 33:28.200
All technology is just a tool.

33:28.680 --> 33:29.720
You have to see with your own eyes,

33:29.720 --> 33:30.510
experience with your own heart,

33:30.510 --> 33:31.960
and keep innovating.

33:31.960 --> 33:33.720
When I was young
and opened my braised food shop,

33:33.720 --> 33:36.480
I made my first big break

33:36.480 --> 33:37.920
by learning from others' approach.

33:37.920 --> 33:39.630
-Right.
-"Learning"?

33:39.970 --> 33:41.960
You literally went to your competitor,
bought their marinade,

33:41.960 --> 33:42.750
used it for your own products,

33:42.750 --> 33:44.640
and ended up putting them out of business,
didn't you?

33:44.640 --> 33:46.110
I... Did I make money or not?

33:46.110 --> 33:47.270
-You did.
-See?

33:47.270 --> 33:49.800
That's what you call
fighting fire with fire.

33:51.440 --> 33:53.640
Don't just stand there. Go take photos.

33:55.350 --> 33:57.080
Why are you taking photos of me?

34:02.720 --> 34:03.920
Haven't you seen enough of me?

34:03.920 --> 34:05.350
Take photos of the environment

34:05.350 --> 34:06.550
and the bookshelves.

34:06.720 --> 34:07.720
For an immersive experience,

34:07.720 --> 34:09.000
you have to sink in, right?

34:09.000 --> 34:11.530
I'll sink. I'll sink all the way
to the bottom.

34:16.590 --> 34:18.110
You're the elder here,

34:18.110 --> 34:19.440
yet you keep toying with him all day.

34:19.440 --> 34:20.770
Is it really fun for you?

34:21.880 --> 34:23.139
Feeling sorry for him?

34:29.920 --> 34:31.400
This one's not bad then.

35:18.710 --> 35:19.710
This flower...

35:22.960 --> 35:24.220
I saw it in a flower shop

35:24.760 --> 35:26.400
and thought it suited you,

35:27.360 --> 35:28.360
so I bought it.

35:33.550 --> 35:35.010
"A gentleman and a maiden,

35:35.190 --> 35:37.050
laughing and teasing each other,

35:37.110 --> 35:39.170
presenting each other with a peony."

35:40.150 --> 35:41.030
That's right.

35:44.400 --> 35:46.060
That's quite romantic of you.

35:46.150 --> 35:47.280
But do you know

35:47.280 --> 35:49.680
that peonies have another meaning as well?

35:49.840 --> 35:52.440
They can also symbolize
the sorrow of parting.

35:58.510 --> 36:00.670
Let's go on a date, Coach Wang.

36:01.600 --> 36:02.890
♪ Time's passing by ♪

36:03.530 --> 36:05.570
♪ Nothing remains ♪

36:06.510 --> 36:09.290
♪ All the dreamers awake alone ♪

36:09.790 --> 36:11.650
♪ Shadows above ♪

36:12.270 --> 36:14.430
♪ Rain falls around ♪

36:14.560 --> 36:15.720
♪ In your arms ♪

36:16.190 --> 36:17.660
♪ We become one ♪

36:16.840 --> 36:19.000
Did I jump the gun there?

36:18.440 --> 36:20.100
♪ Through day and night ♪

36:20.850 --> 36:22.150
♪ I can see you ♪

36:22.440 --> 36:23.280
Whatever.

36:33.320 --> 36:34.510
I think it might be sick.

36:34.510 --> 36:35.710
It just threw up on me.

36:37.590 --> 36:39.070
I know there's a pet hospital nearby.

36:39.070 --> 36:40.280
Let's take it there right away.

36:40.280 --> 36:40.840
Okay.

36:42.400 --> 36:43.200
It's alright.

36:44.000 --> 36:45.200
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

36:50.760 --> 36:51.820
The doctor's here.

36:53.760 --> 36:55.510
Ivory's test report is out.

36:55.960 --> 36:58.150
Based on its blood test results,

36:58.150 --> 36:59.280
Ivory's condition

36:59.280 --> 37:02.070
is consistent with
the symptoms of acute gastroenteritis.

37:02.070 --> 37:03.070
In that case,

37:03.070 --> 37:04.280
Ivory will need to stay
at the hospital tonight

37:04.280 --> 37:06.440
for IV treatment.

37:07.530 --> 37:10.060
We've already arranged treatment
for Ivory.

37:10.070 --> 37:11.960
If you're really worried,
you can stay at the hospital

37:11.960 --> 37:14.510
and keep Ivory company
while it receives the IV infusion.

37:14.510 --> 37:15.880
Okay, thank you.

37:16.840 --> 37:19.230
Ivory, poor thing.

37:19.630 --> 37:20.800
Don't be afraid.

37:20.800 --> 37:22.400
We are here with you.

37:52.400 --> 37:54.590
Ivory, you've suffered a lot.

38:12.280 --> 38:14.320
Dad, Mom.

38:20.710 --> 38:21.630
Who is this?

38:24.070 --> 38:25.400
Hello, Mr. and Mrs. Lin.

38:25.440 --> 38:28.170
I'm Lin Wanxing's tenant
and colleague, Wang Fa.

38:28.480 --> 38:29.880
I live on the third floor.

38:35.550 --> 38:37.000
What brings you guys here?

38:37.000 --> 38:37.920
Wanxing.

38:38.110 --> 38:40.230
How could you, a girl, go out

38:40.230 --> 38:41.760
wearing pajamas
in the middle of the night?

38:41.760 --> 38:42.890
It was an emergency.

38:43.400 --> 38:45.550
He's Coach Wang
of our school's football team.

38:45.550 --> 38:46.590
His dog got sick,

38:46.590 --> 38:48.050
so we went to the hospital.

38:52.590 --> 38:53.650
Coach Wang, right?

38:54.280 --> 38:56.130
Please go back first.

38:56.320 --> 38:58.450
I have something to say to my daughter.

39:08.420 --> 39:09.530
Ms. Lin.

39:11.070 --> 39:12.820
I need to talk to you about something

39:12.820 --> 39:14.550
concerning the football team.

39:16.550 --> 39:19.000
Do you have to talk about it now?

39:20.800 --> 39:21.910
It's quite urgent.

39:22.070 --> 39:23.900
If we don't talk about it today,
it might be too late.

39:23.900 --> 39:24.610
You...

39:28.800 --> 39:30.110
Since it's work,

39:30.480 --> 39:32.140
you two go ahead and talk then.

39:33.670 --> 39:35.000
We're going to visit

39:35.310 --> 39:37.190
Grandpa and Grandma's graves
tomorrow morning at 9.

39:37.190 --> 39:37.990
Don't be late.

39:52.150 --> 39:53.010
Are you hungry?

39:53.190 --> 39:54.190
Want some wontons?

39:54.190 --> 39:54.880
I'm tired.

39:55.630 --> 39:56.590
I want to go rest.

40:04.110 --> 40:04.590
Okay.

40:06.320 --> 40:07.520
Then have a good rest.

40:40.120 --> 40:41.030
Ivory, good dog.

40:41.030 --> 40:42.560
Come on, look at the camera.

40:42.590 --> 40:44.440
You don't feel sick anymore, do you?

40:44.440 --> 40:45.510
Say hi to Wanxing.

40:57.140 --> 40:59.620
[Superstar Slacker]

40:57.760 --> 41:00.620
Make sure it doesn't eat things
it shouldn't again.

41:05.820 --> 41:08.220
[Make sure it doesn't eat things
it shouldn't again.]

41:08.070 --> 41:09.030
Ms. Lin.

41:10.360 --> 41:11.820
I'll go with you tomorrow.

41:14.000 --> 41:15.510
This is not a question.

41:16.030 --> 41:17.760
It's an affirmative sentence.

41:26.250 --> 41:27.140
[Make sure it doesn't eat things
it shouldn't again.]

41:27.160 --> 41:28.170
[Got it.]

41:28.220 --> 41:28.820
Got it.

42:08.140 --> 42:10.140
Why did you bring an outsider along?

42:18.400 --> 42:21.360
Mr. Wang, this is a family matter today.

42:21.360 --> 42:22.290
-You…
-Mrs. Lin.

42:22.710 --> 42:24.280
It was rush hour,
and Wanxing couldn't get a cab,

42:24.280 --> 42:26.550
so she hitched a ride here with me
at the last minute.

42:26.550 --> 42:27.880
Sorry we are late.

42:29.070 --> 42:31.840
You should have anticipated the traffic
before leaving

42:31.840 --> 42:33.500
instead of troubling others.

42:34.920 --> 42:35.980
It's getting late.

42:36.280 --> 42:36.810
Let's go.

43:11.400 --> 43:13.420
[Tomb of the Late Honored Father, Mr. Lin Xunya,
and the Late Honored Mother, Ms. Shen Shuyuan]

43:39.820 --> 43:43.290
[Tomb of the Late Honored Father, Mr. Lin Xunya,
and the Late Honored Mother, Ms. Shen Shuyuan]

43:48.030 --> 43:48.800
Wanxing.

43:49.840 --> 43:51.400
Is it true

43:51.670 --> 43:53.000
that you're not working

43:53.280 --> 43:55.210
as a teacher at Hongjing No. 8 High,

43:55.440 --> 43:56.900
but as a warehouse keeper?

43:59.110 --> 43:59.800
It's true.

44:02.670 --> 44:04.670
Are you... doing this just to make us mad?

44:04.670 --> 44:05.280
Mom,

44:06.840 --> 44:08.770
do you have to talk about this here?

44:09.320 --> 44:10.070
Wanxing.

44:10.640 --> 44:11.650
I know

44:11.880 --> 44:13.940
you're still mad with your dad and me,

44:14.920 --> 44:17.030
but that's no excuse for you to do this.

44:17.030 --> 44:18.430
I'm doing just fine here.

44:20.030 --> 44:21.160
Staying in Hongjing

44:22.840 --> 44:24.300
was Grandpa's dying wish.

44:27.710 --> 44:30.360
But he wouldn't want you
to waste your life like this.

44:30.360 --> 44:31.920
Come back with us

44:31.920 --> 44:33.250
and find a suitable job.

44:33.760 --> 44:35.030
I have your principal's number.

44:35.030 --> 44:36.360
I'll call him right now.

44:36.920 --> 44:38.400
Sorry, I didn't mean it.

44:43.480 --> 44:44.070
Mr. Lin.

44:47.360 --> 44:48.640
Wanxing.

44:59.500 --> 45:02.320
[Tomb of the Late Honored Father, Mr. Lin Xunya,
and the Late Honored Mother, Ms. Shen Shuyuan]
